{"tid":287381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：過去5年，政綱一一落實","createTime":"2017-06-17T11:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T13:46:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8642f2e27f52c15dbdc7ef9293c346f9459d64d7","tid":287381,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170617/s00001/197ce8c8adeddd368af113cc047371a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170617%2Fs00001%2F197ce8c8adeddd368af113cc047371a3.jpg&h=e84e4012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府換屆在即，特首梁振英與法定組織及諮詢委員會主席在禮賓府茶敘，又稱「過去五年，政綱一一落實」。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英晚上於facebook上載在禮賓府拍攝的大合照，指「過去5年，政綱一一落實」，除了問責團隊和整體公務員同事努力，還要感謝各個法定組織及諮詢委員會主席的幫忙，故今天請了數十位法定組織及諮詢委員會主席到禮賓府，「親自感謝他們」。<br />\n<br />\n立法會昨亦為梁振英舉行餞別午宴，多個司局長、行會成員及建制派議員出席，民主派議員則無出席。梁振英表示，感謝立法會支持、配合及監督，又說行政和立法互動過程中，可能有些不太享受，但成果是市民可以享受。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英另提到，卸任前是最忙的1個月，因為將會發表施政匯報，總結過去5年政府工作。"},{"pid":"3bb7e6fb2537bd748c7a1f236bb2e50f7377a6e7","tid":287381,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170617/s00001/1497697616409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170617%2Fs00001%2F1497697616409&d=ul4agu%2FHNv9oOMaDIRQ9U%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=86451223\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170617%2Fs00001%2F1497697616409&h=0fcada52\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170617/s00001/1497697616409</a>"},{"pid":"f9e7f6151a83d18d97eb0da445646a923ae805d5","tid":287381,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9571bda48cfe3ed7e0c39151a3ce13c7bd7737a","tid":287381,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0